In [[11 ABY/Legends|11 ABY]], [[Admiral/Legends|Admiral]] [[Llon Banjeer]] commanded one of the largest '''fleets''' in the [[Imperial Navy/Legends|Imperial Navy]]. The [[Fleet/Legends|fleet]] was presumably this which led him to be assigned to the [[Imperial Ruling Council/Legends|Interim Ruling Council]] by [[Carnor Jax]].

